Onions are excellent. I love them raw, sliced thin on sandwiches or in salads, caramelized, on tacos, in French onion soup, pretty much everywhere.For a long time I thought I disliked onion rings. Then I had incredible onion rings at a pub one night and realized that I loved excellent onion rings, I'd just been receiving crap onion rings up until that point.
