I do not like the taste of onions. Generally, the closer they are to raw and solitary, the less I like them in my food. I like them fine in salsa, or ok caramelized in a dish, and just barely in onion rings, but added as a separate item they are a no-go. Burgers, sandwiches, pizza, chili dogs. I will order them without. If I get them, I may remove them, depending on how difficult it is or how much is on there.
