Aromatics are a wonderful thing, onions included. In fact I don't think I've had an onion I don't like. Rare is the dish I make that doesn't have onions involved. Tomato sauce for pasta, or pizza? Onions. Chili? Onions, Tacos/Fajitas? Onions. Steak? Onions. Burgers? Onions. Crock Pot Pulled Pork? Barbeque Sauce and Onions. Roast Chicken? Onions.Short of cereal I'm not sure what I make that doesn't have onions in it. Hell even my home fries and omelettes have onions in them.
